# Vite build output (regenerate with `npm run build` from frontend/ — see README.md).
#
# The wwwroot/ files currently committed are a prebuilt snapshot so the sample runs
# out-of-box without a Node toolchain. A fresh `npm run build` emits new content-hashed
# asset filenames; those are intentionally NOT committed (they would silently drift from
# frontend/src and be unreviewable in diffs). Rebuild locally to pick up frontend changes.
wwwroot/assets/
wwwroot/index.html

# Node / build artifacts
node_modules/
*.tsbuildinfo
